  "texts": [
    "Models 1 and 2 use as a dependent variable whether an invention receives investment, and Models 3 and 4 whether the TTO files at least one patent.",
    "The average commercial potential of the articles tied to an invention strongly predicts both variables.",
    "Furthermore, we analyze whether an invention leads to commercial agreements (Model 5) and licensing deals (6); is commercialized via a Startup (7) and commercialized via a Startup with VC funds (8); and generates revenue (9).",
    "All dependent variables are binary indicators.",
    "We add controls for the author's previous experience disclosing inventions to the TTO (binary) as well as for the authors' scientific prominence at time t -1 (log(H-index t-1 + 1))."
  ],
